data.name: Label35.Text
data.value: Activate this option will encrypt all your accounts' passwords in the database. You will have to choose a KEY that won't be stored anywhere. When you will load the application, you will be asked for the key to decrypt the passwords. Warning: if you change this option, you have to re-encode the passwords for your existing accounts.
